definitions.definition: To perform a practical joke on; to trick and make a fool of someone.

subdefinitions.definition: To make a prank call to (someone).

definitions.definition: To call someone's phone and hang up before they answer , so as to send them a notification (of a missed call ) without incurring fees .
examples: Hey man, prank me when you wanna get picked up.
I don't have your number in my phone; can you prank me?

definitions.definition: To adorn in a showy manner; to dress or equip ostentatiously .

main_definition: ( transitive ) To perform a practical joke on; to trick and make a fool of someone.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , slang ) To call someone's phone and hang up before they answer , so as to send them a notification (of a missed call ) without incurring fees .
( transitive , archaic ) To adorn in a showy manner; to dress or equip ostentatiously .
( intransitive ) To make an ostentatious show .
